flowchart TD
    A[Config text or uploaded file] --> B[ConfLoader.deploy]
    B --> C[Close current GenericConfig]
    C --> D{Full replacement?}
    D -- yes --> E[Clear TopicManager]
    D -- no --> F[Keep existing topics]
    E --> G[Write config_files/uploaded.conf]
    F --> G
    G --> H[GenericConfig.create]
    H --> I[Read non-empty trimmed lines]
    I --> J{Line count divisible by 3?}
    J -- no --> X[Reject config]
    J -- yes --> K[Validate unique publishers]
    K --> L[Load class by reflection]
    L --> M[Call String[], String[] constructor]
    M --> N[Wrap in ParallelAgent]
    N --> O[Move registrations to wrapper]
    O --> P[Active graph ready]
